  <!-- EN: Quest expired: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>Завдання більше не актуальне: [resolvedQuestName]</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The bandit camp has packed up and moved on. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has expired. -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>Бандити зібрали свій табір та рушили далі. Завдання "[resolvedQuestName]" більше не актуальне.</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>Завдання провалено: [resolvedQuestName]</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: After being discovered, the bandit camp has dispersed. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has ended. -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>Ворожий табір було виявлено та розгромлено. Завдання "[resolvedQuestName]" більше не актуальне..</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Payment arrived -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelPaymentArrived.slateRef>Винагороду отримано</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelPaymentArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: You have defeated the bandit camp!\n\nThe payment from [asker_faction_name] has arrived. -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextPaymentArrived.slateRef>Ви розгромили ворожий табір!\n\nНадійшла винагорода від [asker_faction_name].</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextPaymentArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelFavorReceiver.slateRef>[asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterLabelFavorReceiver.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: These colonists participated in the victory for the quest [resolvedQuestName]. [asker_definite] wants to know who should receive the [royalFavorReward_amount] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] for this service. -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextFavorReceiver.slateRef>Ці колоністи приймали участь у виконанні завдання "[resolvedQuestName]". [asker_definite] хоче знати, кому належить призначити [royalFavorReward_amount] од. [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] за свою службу.</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.LetterTextFavorReceiver.slateRef>
  
